Spell ideas. A few things to make the matter spec viable:<P>Cloak of invisiblitity (matter spec)<BR>Acts as stealth at the spec level of the matter spec. Speed penalty decreases with level. Something like:<BR>10   Minor Cloak of invisibility   Duration 3 mins<BR>17   Cloak of invisiblity    Duration 6 mins<BR>25   Greater cloak of invisibility    9 mins<BR>etc...<P>Telekinetic burst (Matter spec)<BR>Single target, causes target to move a distance in a random direction. Breaks /stick etc if they have it. Distance moved increases as spec increases, start with very small distance.<P>Mind shield (Mind spec)<BR>Obtained at 28 spec in mind. Acts as blade turn for mind magic attack. This includes mezmerize (but not root or stun). Alternatively could be %resistance increase to mind magic, increasing at several spell / spec levels.<P>--------------------<P>Yosarian<BR>Sorcerer lvl 40<BR>Dragon's Shadow Guild - Nimue
